<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空悄悄地看了一下红孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>剑包围了红孩儿，每把剑都对着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把这些剑拿开！”红孩儿大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只要你听话。”观音菩萨说，“我就放了你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我保证！”红孩儿大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你让我做什么，我就做什么！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨念了个咒。那些剑都消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿非常生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“观音菩萨，小心！”悟空大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿朝着观音菩萨冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到了红孩儿面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空正要去打红孩儿时，观音菩萨拿出了五个金属环。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把它们扔向红孩儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>套住了他的脑袋、手腕和脚踝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这妖怪！”观音菩萨说，“居然敢打我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>红孩儿一动不能动，生气地看着观音菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空举起了金箍棒要打红孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！”观音菩萨说，“不要伤害他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会带他回普陀山做我的弟子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，观音菩萨。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨拿着净瓶飞到地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她念了个咒，所有的水都退回了净瓶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，观音菩萨就带着红孩儿向南飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空走进了红孩儿的洞穴，解开了唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又找到了八戒，解开了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这三个人下了山，找到了悟净。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一行人继续往西走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就这样，几个月过去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，他们走到了一条宽阔的大河边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们又要过河了。”八戒不高兴地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这一路上有很多河的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空说，“我们都得过。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要怎么过这条河呢？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，对面来了一条小船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船上有一个男人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人一边划船，一边看着唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们好！”那个男人说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要过河吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们正在想要怎么过河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要去西天取经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是唐僧？”男人高兴地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说你们一定会经过这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”男人微笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你很有名。”他低头看了一眼小船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很愿意帮你们过河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是你们也看到了，我的船不大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我一次只能带两个人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人说话的时候，悟空仔细地看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个男人有些奇怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空正要说什么，八戒向前走了一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父和我先过河。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空想了一下。“师父，我觉得有些奇怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧皱起眉头说：“悟空，你从不相信别人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个好心人是要帮我们过河的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空咬着嘴唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧和八戒上了小船，坐在船里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小船离开了河岸。悟空看着小船划向对岸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当小船走到河中央的时候，悟空注意到了什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我看错了，还是那条船真的在下沉？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净看了看。“你没看错。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那条船真的在下沉！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看着小船渐渐地沉到了河下面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空气得直跺脚。“我就觉得很奇怪！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人抓走了师父和八戒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>